{"tid":1364744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人將反對遊行呢單野發俾外國媒體？","createTime":"2019-07-25T12:19:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T13:36:16.000Z","uid":35382,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d2be751170105aada7c761dc1bc9e180e14c8f3c","tid":1364744,"uid":35382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:19:57.000Z","msg":"而家我地香港連最基本既遊行 集會既權利<br />\n都俾人剝削 隨意踐踏<br />\n我地究竟仲要失去到點既地步<br />\n先識得去反抗 <br />\n所以而家希望眾巴絲可以打封信<br />\n告知外國媒體 <br />\n而家香港面對港共既暴政 港共既橫蠻<br />\n完全視香港人既權利如無物<br />\n而家港共竟然怕左堆牛屎佬<br />\n就唔俾遊行 剝削香港人應有權利<br />\n官警黑勾結 <br />\n而家就係最需要俾更多外國媒體知道<br />\n我地香港人既自由已受到嚴重既打壓<br />\n自問小弟英語唔好 無法打到一封靚既文<br />\n所以在此懇求有識之士打封信俾外國媒體<br />\n&ldquo;自由&rdquo;2字已被港共狗狠狠踐踏 謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fccd3f6f1eb9e4fed335790bc2589e6bbc26928","tid":1364744,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:20:36.000Z","msg":"[緊急，星期六悼念]李鵬未死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1364610\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1364610</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫手推 太少人識鄧炳強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2135057d98cdd96a7f989844639302a72289e4ac","tid":1364744,"uid":35382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:20:41.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9de562a57eed5a8739b0e99d175200e4286bb59","tid":1364744,"uid":35382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:21:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03894ad6f9a2972e86871c09af8d426f9ce0c5e6","tid":1364744,"uid":35382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:21:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji